    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate</p><p>Crack your<strong> egg[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into a shallow bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>to another plate</p><p>Coat the<strong> seasoned hake</strong> in the<strong> flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add it into the <strong>beaten egg</strong> and finally press it into the <strong>panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1713871709722-x200.jpg",
