    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the hake is cooking, heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to break down</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs, then add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until thickened</p>",
